    <!-- HowTo -->
    <string name="howto_title">🛠 How to enable ADB debugging</string>
    <string name="howto_adb_active">✅ ADB Debugging: ACTIVE — You\'re ready!</string>
    <string name="howto_adb_inactive">❌ ADB Debugging: INACTIVE — Follow the guide below</string>
    <string name="howto_open_dev_options">Open Developer Options</string>
    <string name="howto_check_dev_options">Check developer options</string>
    <string name="howto_step1_title">Step 1 — Enable Developer Options</string>
    <string name="howto_step1_desc">Go to: Settings → About\n→ Tap 7 times on \"Build number\"\n\nThe message \"You are now a developer!\" will appear.</string>
    <string name="howto_step2_title">Step 2 — Enable ADB Debugging</string>
    <string name="howto_step2_desc">Go to: Settings → Developer Options\n→ Enable \"ADB Debugging\"\n\nOr use the button above to access it directly.</string>
    <string name="howto_step3_title">Step 3 — Authorize the connection</string>
    <string name="howto_step3_desc">When first activating DNS via ADB, a popup \"Allow USB debugging?\" may appear.\n\n→ Check \"Always allow from this device\"\n→ Press OK\n\nThe app will then automatically remember the connection.</string>
    <string name="howto_note_tv_title">💡 Note for Thomson boxes / Android TV</string>
    <string name="howto_note_tv_desc">On most Android TV boxes, ADB port 5555 is locally accessible. You just need ADB debugging enabled in developer options — no USB cable or PC needed.</string>
    <string name="howto_firestick_title">🔥 Firestick / Fire TV</string>
    <string name="howto_firestick_desc">On Firestick, the ADB auto-connect method often doesn\'t work. It is recommended to use the VPN method which works without configuration.\n\nIf you still want to use ADB:\n1. Install ADB on a PC (platform-tools)\n2. Connect to the Firestick:\n   adb connect FIRESTICK_IP:5555\n3. Grant the permission:\n   adb shell pm grant net.appstorefr.perfectdnsmanager android.permission.WRITE_SECURE_SETTINGS\n4. After that, the app can change DNS directly.</string>
    <string name="howto_recommendation_title">✅ Recommendation</string>
    <string name="howto_recommendation_desc">The VPN method is the simplest: it works on all devices without any special configuration. It creates a local VPN that only redirects DNS queries to the server of your choice.</string>

